                                <condition/>
		    </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout><p>The text is laid out on the right hand wall (as one enters) of the roughly rectangular chamber. Two sequences of letters run in the upper line from left to right and in the lower line from right to left, with a final letter below.</p>
